<body>
    <div class="wrap">
        <header>
            <a class="brand" href="/">ZenPak</a>
        </header>

        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="meta">Last updated: 2026-07-06 · FX Bénard, auto-entrepreneur (France)</p>

        <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
        <p>ZenPak (<a href="https://zenpak.app">zenpak.app</a>) is operated by FX Bénard, a French auto-entrepreneur (SIRET on file). Contact: <a href="mailto:info@zenpak.app">info@zenpak.app</a>.</p>

        <h2>2. Data we collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account data</strong> — username, email address, hashed password.</li>
            <li><strong>Gear content</strong> — pack lists, items, categories, weights, and prices you create.</li>
            <li><strong>Billing data</strong> — subscription status and period. Payment details (card numbers, etc.) are handled exclusively by <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Stripe</a> and never stored on our servers.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage logs</strong> — server access logs (IP address, timestamp, URL) retained for up to 90 days for security and debugging.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How we use your data</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide and improve the ZenPak service.</li>
            <li>To send transactional emails (password reset, email verification). We do not send marketing emails without explicit consent.</li>
            <li>To process subscription payments via Stripe.</li>
            <li>To detect and prevent abuse.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your data. We share data only with:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — for payment processing (their <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">privacy policy</a> applies).</li>
            <li><strong>Mailgun</strong> — for transactional emails.</li>
            <li><strong>Cloudinary</strong> — for item image hosting (images you upload).</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Public lists you choose to share are accessible to anyone with the link.</p>

        <h2>5. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <p>If you are in the EU/EEA, you have the right to access, correct, export, or delete your personal data. To exercise these rights, email <a href="mailto:info@zenpak.app">info@zenpak.app</a>. You may also delete your account directly from the Account settings page — this removes all your data from our servers within 30 days.</p>

        <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use a single session cookie (<code>lp</code>) to keep you logged in. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>

        <h2>7. Data retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active. After account deletion, personal data is purged within 30 days. Anonymised usage statistics may be retained indefinitely.</p>

        <h2>8. Security</h2>
        <p>Passwords are stored as bcrypt hashes. All data in transit is encrypted via HTTPS. We apply industry-standard security practices, but no system is 100% secure.</p>

        <h2>9. Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy. Material changes will be announced via email or an in-app notice. Continued use of ZenPak after the effective date constitutes acceptance.</p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:info@zenpak.app">info@zenpak.app</a>.</p>

        <footer>
            <span>© 2026 FX Bénard — ZenPak</span>
            <span>
                <a href="/">Home</a> ·
                <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a> ·
                <a href="mailto:info@zenpak.app">Contact</a>
            </span>
        </footer>
    </div>
